/**
 * Restores an EdgeTypeName object from its string representation.
 * This method parses a string representation of an edge type name (in the format 
 * "sourceVertex__edgeLabel__targetVertex") and reconstructs the corresponding EdgeTypeName object.
 *
 * @param edgeName The string representation of the edge type name to be restored
 * @return An EdgeTypeName object reconstructed from the string representation
 * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the edgeName format is invalid (doesn't contain exactly 3 parts)
