/**
 * Determines if write protection is enabled for the current request method based on service policy.
 * 
 * This method extracts the live policy from the service policy if available, and checks
 * if write protection is enabled for the current HTTP request method.
 * 
 * @param servicePolicy The service policy to evaluate for write protection settings
